### Staff Management API - REST Client
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### 1. GET All Staff
GET {{baseUrl}}/staffs
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. CREATE New Staff
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/add
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "mobileNumber": "01712345678",
  "permissions": {
    "createInvoice": true,
    "editInvoice": true,
    "deleteInvoice": false,
    "cashmemo": true,
    "uploadReport": false
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### 3. GET Single Staff by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### 4. UPDATE Staff
PUT {{baseUrl}}/staff/edit/698c432ab24c050d9011686f
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "mobileNumber": "01712345679",
  "permissions": {
    "createInvoice": true,
    "editInvoice": true,
    "deleteInvoice": true,
    "cashmemo": true,
    "uploadReport": true
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### 5. DEACTIVATE Staff
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f/deactivate

### 6. ACTIVATE Staff
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f/activate

### 7. DELETE Staff (Hard Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
